data.description: Searching for a tranquil residence in a serene neighborhood of Ball? Welcome to 5937 Tall Pine Drive! This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home spans an impressive 1,600 square feet, presenting an ideal opportunity for first-time homebuyers or families. The layout of this home is thoughtfully designed, providing easy access to each room. Moreover, the property rests on nearly half an acre, offering an abundance of outdoor space. However, the true highlight is the expansive patio area that invites you to unwind and savor your morning coffee, with the comfort of ceiling fans and welcoming rocking chairs. This home creates a setting for relaxation and enjoying the neighborhood of Tall Pine Drive.
